      "title": "Four drown in Nilwala River",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Four men have gone missing from a group of people who went to bathe at Udaha Ella, Nilwala River in Pitabeddara this evening, police said.",
        "The victims were part of a group of people who were working in a private company in Midigama and had gone to bathe after joining a party in Akuressa."
